3_Density_Analysis.Rmd\
\
This script provides the analysis for answering questions related to urchin densities. \
	(1) What are the mean sea urchin densities across treatments? \
	(2) Did urchin densities vary significantly across months? Across sites? \
	(3) Were there significant differences in urchin densities between open and caged  \
	      treatments? \
	\
\
Determines the mean depths of sites, including the shallowest and deepest site. \
Determines if urchin densities are statistically different from each other across sites. \
Determine mean urchin densities by site \
Visualizes urchin counts over transects \
\
	Inputs\
		- cleaned_monitoring_transects.csv\
		- cleaned_green_gravel_monitoring.csv\
		- density_urchin_transects.csv\
\
	Outputs\
		- densities_by_sp.png (stacked bar chart of sp by site)\
